===Noun===
'''maru'''
#A suffix of Japanese ship names. ''The Nippon Maru''
#(''linguistics'', ''colloquial'') A [[diacritic]] ( ゜ ) used with Japanese [[kana]] to change an ''h'' to a ''p''.
#A large, circular [[punctuation]] mark ( 。 ) used as a [[full stop]] in Japanese text.
